{"tid":2159333,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果免費頒個榮譽博士學位比你,要唔要？","createTime":"2020-08-16T09:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T09:14:08.000Z","uid":210755,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9803a8cd2edeb6ec06edc1e88bf2db90a9ba83e3","tid":2159333,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:12:28.000Z","msg":"柒𠹌到...林肯定含𠹌大學......貼錢都唔要.....<br />\n嘜𠹌野諾貝爾獎學人系列榮譽嘜柒<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/2383520905194645/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F2383520905194645%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=4f20254b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/2383520905194645/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yq5Y66C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyq5Y66C.jpg&h=66487140&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8ZK2EZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8ZK2EZ.jpg&h=ce32f06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7i70rF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7i70rF.jpg&h=2b5ad041&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdmNfZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhdmNfZ2.jpg&h=eade21df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V8enPj4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV8enPj4.jpg&h=14807c62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y7Df9j5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy7Df9j5.jpg&h=700f3c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20180820/s00001/1534761149954/【emily-online】健身「一代宗師」成諾貝爾獎學人-網民熱賀胡力威「升呢」做榮譽教授\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534761149954%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%97%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%B3%80%E8%83%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%87%E5%91%A2%E3%80%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJB%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=87132954\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20180820%2Fs00001%2F1534761149954%2F%E3%80%90emily-online%E3%80%91%E5%81%A5%E8%BA%AB%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%AE%97%E5%B8%AB%E3%80%8D%E6%88%90%E8%AB%BE%E8%B2%9D%E7%88%BE%E7%8D%8E%E5%AD%B8%E4%BA%BA-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%B3%80%E8%83%A1%E5%8A%9B%E5%A8%81%E3%80%8C%E5%8D%87%E5%91%A2%E3%80%8D%E5%81%9A%E6%A6%AE%E8%AD%BD%E6%95%99%E6%8E%88&h=eaba59b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20180820/s00001/1534761149954/【emily-online】健身「一代宗師」成諾貝爾獎學人-網民熱賀胡力威「升呢」做榮譽教授</a><br />\n力威健身中心喺facebook專頁更換頭像，宣布公司創辦人胡力威躋身2018年度諾貝爾獎學人系列，成為加拿大特許管理學院榮譽院士及榮譽教授。網民紛紛致賀。<br />\n<br />\n其實頒獎禮早於上月21舉行，近日胡教授喺佢一手創辨「力威健身學院」facebook專頁轉相，大家先知道消息。專頁「關於」嗰欄都要加返「教授」二字，認真威水。當日片段顯示，胡教授穿上院士袍，收起彪形大漢形象，親手接過由前食衛局長高永文代表頒授嘅獎項。<br />\n<br />\n胡教授健身界「一代宗師」名銜非浪得虛名，近40年健身經驗自創多套理論，其教學之道將健身與人生結合，啟發上千門生。早年佢喺訪問中表示：「人生沒有掙扎的話，和街市的死魚沒兩樣，人生、心靈上都要掙扎，不掙扎不強大。」<br />\n<br />\n亞洲知識管理學院官方網頁顯示，頒授典禮喺亞洲國際博覽館舉行，殊榮及獎項均是頒給來自不同界別的社會賢達及翹楚。當晚有過千名社會名流及嘉賓出席，場面非常盛大。"},{"pid":"f68b4e2549c69e97c57adba660d9b82325cbb94a","tid":2159333,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BLh8KTZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBLh8KTZ.jpg&h=e3ab1c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhyDnFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhyDnFG.jpg&h=88efaa5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd1bda9476efba27488be882e413fb8404470b8d","